<m0>   Going to a beach resort? <m1> <m0>The most versatile travel item you can have is a sarong. <m1> <m0>In a pinch, it converts to a beach blanket, a tropical dress or skirt, an evening shawl, an accessorizing scarf, protection against mosquitoes in the early evening, a lightweight blanket and, in emergencies, even a towel.<ql>
